      "paragraph_name": "5500-READ-AUTH-SUMMRY",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph reads the pending authorization summary from the IMS database. It moves the XREF-ACCT-ID to PA-ACCT-ID and then executes a DLI GU (Get Unique) command to retrieve the PAUTSUM0 segment into PENDING-AUTH-SUMMARY. The paragraph evaluates the DIBSTAT to determine if the read was successful. If the segment is found, FOUND-PAUT-SMRY-SEG is set to TRUE. If the segment is not found, NFOUND-PAUT-SMRY-SEG is set to TRUE. If any other error occurs during the read, an error message is logged with 9500-LOG-ERROR, and ERR-CRITICAL and ERR-IMS flags are set. The IMS PCB number is PAUT-PCB-NUM.",
